                    <div class="row mb-5">
                        <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-lg-4 card-videos mb-4 ">
                            <h2 class="text-white">Videos In Aymara</h2>
                            <p>The videos published in this section are all presented in the Aymara language. These
                                teach
                                concepts of biology through the lens of everyday life examples. This helps to generate a
                                greater sense of understanding among Aymara-speakers. Each video has a simple
                                explanation as
                                well as an interesting fact that enriches the information being communicated.
                            </p>

                        </div>
                        <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-lg-8">
                            <video src="https://2021.igem.org/wiki/images/2/2b/T--Bolivia--inclusivityVideoFinal.mp4"
                                id="video1" controls
