                    <div class="row mb-5">

                        <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-lg-4 mb-4  card-videos">
                            <h2 class="text-white">Videos In Quechua</h2>
                            <p>With the support of charismatic presenters, the videos in Quechua were well received by
                                the
                                different social network communities of iGEM Bolivia.
                            </p>
                            <p>
                                Something to highlight in the Quechua video section is that there are Quechua-speakers
                                from
                                different parts of the country. Because of this, appreciation for different accents
                                belonging to various regions can be observed in all of the videos.
